  the SLOT) to resolve a blocker.
  (http://forums.gentoo.org/viewtopic-p-7389618.html#7389618)

  01 Sep 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> bcmail-1.38-r2.ebuild:
  Marked *-macos

