*bcmail-1.49 (01 Jun 2013)

  01 Jun 2013; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> +bcmail-1.49.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.49, reported by maksbotan; tests are restricted since tests
  for dependencies are restricted, see bug #471998. Dropped ~amd64-fbsd keyword
  since dev-java/bcprov and dev-java/bcpkix have no ~amd64-fbsd keyword, see bug
  #472010.

  12 May 2012; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> bcmail-1.45.ebuild:
  keyword ~amd64-fbsd

  02 Nov 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> bcmail-1.45.ebuild:
  keyword ~x86-fbsd

  28 Aug 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> bcmail-1.45.ebuild:
  Marked ~x64-macos

